metadata.description: In the world of Peaky Birds, these Eggs hold a unique multiplier mechanism, further enhancing their value. Each Egg grants you a 5% increase in rewards earned (max of 5 Eggs) through our new Peaky Travel Rewards App that is currently under construction. Peaky Birds Eggs may also gain access to unique bonuses and rewards exclusive to holders.
metadata.name: Peaky Birds Egg
